dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Inset maps: Isthmus of Panama showing location of railroad and canal -- Map showing railroad between Caracas and La Guayra. Indexes on verso. In upper margin: Rand-McNally indexed atlas. [Colombia and Venezuela]. 326-327.
